        "summary": "List YouTube video assets with watch/embed URLs",
        "description": "Returns YouTube links from Google Ads video assets (not parsed from ad names). Merges ad_group_ad_asset_view (Demand Gen, etc.), classic VIDEO ads, and optional account-level YOUTUBE_VIDEO assets. Intended for ChatGPT Custom Actions.",
